An advanced colorpicker for the Extjs framework.

Simply drop the files into the root of an ExtJs 4.x install folder.

An example page can be found in: INSTALL_DIR/examples/colorpicker.html

usage : 
To create the colorpicker panel:
var colorpicker = Ext.widget('ux.colorpicker', {
	renderTo : Ext.getBody()
});

To create a colorpickerfield : 
var colorpicker = Ext.widget('ux.colorpickerfield', {
	renderTo : Ext.getBody(),
	value : '#000000'
});